data.description: LOCATION LOCATION AND RENOVATED! SUNWAY KNOLLS is one of Sumter's established quiet neighborhoods-Families walk their dogs. BONUS-Neighborhood is big enough for runners, bike riders/golf carts yet this home is located on a quiet cul-de-sac street with no throughway traffic. PRIVACY-no back door neighbors and .80 acres! Sought-after Schools 2 miles away-Alice Drive and Wilson Hall. Sunway Knolls is located in the heart of Sumter-CVS, a coffee shop, and dining just around the corner-Downtown activities are only 2.5 miles away/Shaw AFB 6 just miles away! Best of all is the Recreation room + Wet Bar. Roof 2017-Gas Pac HVAC 2019-All New Vinyl Windows-New R34 Insulation-No Carpet, All Laminate Flooring-2 storage sheds. THE LOT LINE EXTENDS AN ADDITIONAL 120 FT PAST THE BACKYARD FENCE.
